### ‚úÖ Version 0.3.1 - Contact Form Fix (Google Forms Integration)
**Status:** PENDING
**Goal:** Replace contact form with Google Forms integration for static hosting

#### Tasks:
- [ ] **Create Google Form** - Set up form with same fields (name, email, category, subject, message)
- [ ] **Configure Google Form settings** - Enable responses, set up email notifications
- [ ] **Get Google Form embed code** - Extract form URL and embed options
- [ ] **Update ContactView.vue** - Replace current form with Google Forms integration
- [ ] **Style embedded form** - Match Studio 402 branding and design
- [ ] **Add form instructions** - Guide users on form submission and response times
- [ ] **Test form functionality** - Verify submissions work and emails are received
- [ ] **Update contact page content** - Add information about Google Forms usage

#### Google Forms Implementation:
- **Chosen Service:** Google Forms (Free, unlimited submissions)
- **Integration Method:** Embedded iframe with custom styling
- **Backup Option:** Direct link to Google Form if embedding issues occur
- **Email Notifications:** Automatic email alerts for new submissions
- **Response Collection:** Google Sheets integration for response management

#### Benefits of Google Forms:
- ‚úÖ **Free and unlimited** - No submission limits
- ‚úÖ **No external dependencies** - No API keys or accounts needed
- ‚úÖ **Automatic email notifications** - Instant alerts for new submissions
- ‚úÖ **Built-in spam protection** - Google's anti-spam measures
- ‚úÖ **Mobile responsive** - Works perfectly on all devices
- ‚úÖ **Easy management** - View responses in Google Sheets

**Priority:** High - Simple and reliable solution for static hosting

